
        -ROADMAP-

0) Pygame:
    pygame settings and interaction variables
    pygame main loop  (drawing and interaction)

1) Display dev info:
    toggle: info, screen axis, note, mouse pos


2) Music variables:
    chords (interval value)
    scales (note value)
        natural, flat, sharp

    Map note: value


3) display piano keys:
    drawing surface
    draw keys


4) Class Button:
    .draw()
    .write() if text button
    .ispressed()


5) User input variable:
    input note
    input chord


6) Detect mouse input:
    get pressed key
    get mouse input
    store input note
    display input note


7) Display chord buttons:
    drawing surface
    draw buttons


8) Detect mouse input:
    get pressed chord
    get mouse input
    store input chord
    display input chord


9) Highlight pressed keys
10) Highlight pressed chord

11) Bonus features:
    display note on music staff



        -Piano Chord-

settings and interaction variables:
    screen width/height, Clock

music variables:

    chords
    scales
    sound list


piano:

    12 keys, black and white
    store mouse input
    highlight pressed key


chords button:

5M 5m 6M 6m 64M 64m 7+ 7M 7m ...


User input:
    input note
    input chord
